3. (C) AIRCRAFT PREFLIGHT - INADEQUATE - PILOT IN COMMAND
4. (C) LANDING GEAR,MAIN GEAR ATTACHMENT - LOSS,TOTAL
----------
Occurrence #2: NOSE OVER
Phase of Operation: TAKEOFF
Findings
5. (F) TERRAIN CONDITION - SOFT
